1. On je doista* prekrasan. (He is truly beautiful.)
2. Doista* se trudim da razumem. (I really am trying to understand.)
3. Doista* ne znam šta da kažem. (I really don't know what to say.)
4. Doista* si me iznenadio. (You really surprised me.)
5. Ona doista* dobro izgleda. (She really looks good.)
6. On je doista* jedinstven. (He is truly unique.)
7. Oni doista* nisu dobri ljudi. (They really are not good people.)
8. Doista* je lep dan. (It really is a nice day.)